-988741832.text: "In addition, assessment of the levels of TNF-alpha, IL-1beta, and IL-10 by ELISA in the heart homogenate of control and pSIRT6 injected mice after TAC or sham surgery showed that SIRT6 significantly attenuated the TAC induced upregulation of TNF-alpha and IL-1beta and the downregulation of IL-10, suggesting that the effect of SIRT6 was mediated by the modulation of inflammatory factors."
